item.title: Mental Health
item.description: Various notes on possible issues to keep in mind. Not Asking For Help: possible cause is none of value, or at all, is believed to be possibly received. Not Being Socially Active: probably due to the fact that if I didn’t feel loved by family, the assumption is that nobody else could love me. If neither my family loved me, why would anybody else do? Why bothering trying to find love in others then?
